♪Never letting go, because of you♪

54
00:04:33,420 --> 00:04:35,760
(Your account received 133,532 yuan
on April 15th.[Baichuan Savings Bank])

55
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:46,600
The senior told me

56
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,630
it was our master's idea.

57
00:04:49,510 --> 00:04:52,310
(This is my investment in you two's life.)

58
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:54,750
(You have to manage your life well)

59
00:04:55,600 --> 00:04:57,430
(to live up to my expectations.)

60
00:04:58,630 --> 00:04:59,190
I gotta go.

61
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:00,240
Where are you going?

62
00:05:01,430 --> 00:05:02,270
To open the restaurant.

63
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:09,390
(Master, I understand what you said.)

64
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:11,920
(I'll give it a really careful thought
to figure out what I really want.)

65
00:05:12,040 --> 00:05:12,630
Good.

66
00:05:13,630 --> 00:05:14,800
I'll wait for you

67
00:05:15,190 --> 00:05:16,160
to tell me your final answer.

68
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:21,680
(Master, I owed you an answer,)

69
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,070
(and now I've finally got one.)

70
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:31,060
(Closure)

71
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,600
(You opened this restaurant
even before the challenge.)

72
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:47,270
(How did you make it?)

73
00:05:47,430 --> 00:05:48,870
(Can you give me more details?)

74
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:52,720
(I'll report you
if you don't show me some real stuff.)

75
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:05,870
Where are you going?

76
00:06:06,560 --> 00:06:08,000
Your class is over,

77
00:06:08,240 --> 00:06:10,270
but your task isn't.

78
00:06:12,510 --> 00:06:13,600
Wake up!

79
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:15,720
Wait.

80
00:06:16,560 --> 00:06:18,120
Chef, I was just kidding.

81
00:06:18,120 --> 00:06:19,120
Teach me one more time.

82
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:41,920
- What are you doing?
- Has everything been take care of?

83
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,120
I let them go

84
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,120
and paid them triple salary.

85
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:48,750
Here is yours.

86
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,750
Jiang Jie,

87
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,560
Chuncheng is not just yours.

88
00:06:57,920 --> 00:07:00,040
From when we decided to go back
to Baichuan to the site selection,

89
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:01,950
all the way until now,

90
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,630
we've been always on the same boat.

91
00:07:05,600 --> 00:07:06,600
Take it.

92
00:07:08,630 --> 00:07:09,630
I did lose.

93
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:12,600
Both you and I are clear about Li Nai.

94
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:15,800
Even if she practices her cooking skills
day and night,

95
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:18,120
she can't possibly exceed you
within such a short term.

96
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,510
What do you want to say?

97
00:07:19,750 --> 00:07:21,390
Both you and Jiang Xuyang know that.

98
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:23,750
Firewood Rice and Cao's Fish
even haven't been kicked out,

99
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:25,950
how could he help the Li family now?

100
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,120
And I did some investigation,

101
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,240
and found out Cui Can

102
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,630
is actually Cui Jing's little brother.

103
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,390
Li Nai wouldn't do it.

104
00:07:39,070 --> 00:07:40,040
You still believe her.

105
00:07:40,190 --> 00:07:41,830
Did you forget she opened a restaurant
behind you,

106
00:07:41,830 --> 00:07:44,390
and tricked you like a fool?

107
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:46,870
It's just because your feeling for her
blinded your eyes

108
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,560
that you ended up like this.

109
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,560
It's not that.

110
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:54,720
Do you really think Cui Jing would take
such a big risk for her little brother?

111
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,720
And this is only your guesswork.

112
00:07:57,870 --> 00:08:00,000
Okay. Let's lay it aside.

113
00:08:00,390 --> 00:08:02,600
As long as you nod, we can start over.

114
00:08:03,390 --> 00:08:06,270
We can make all the details
public through media.

115
00:08:06,470 --> 00:08:07,980
As long as the public opinion
is strong enough,

116
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:10,190
maybe we can compete with
Eating at Dusk again.

117
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:12,870
I'll never believe you'll lose to Li Nai.

118
00:08:13,310 --> 00:08:14,800
And it's never been easy for us.

119
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:17,390
Now it ended up like this.
Is this really what you want?

120
00:08:22,540 --> 00:08:26,380
(Eating at Dusk)

121
00:08:30,360 --> 00:08:32,260
Chef Li, would you answer the questions?

122
00:08:32,270 --> 00:08:34,200
Chef Li, answer my question please.

123
00:08:34,550 --> 00:08:37,720
Chef Li.

124
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,750
Everybody, Chef Li is not available today.

125
00:08:40,750 --> 00:08:42,080
I'll answer your questions.

126
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:45,030
It's said you are Cui Jing's little brother.
Is it true?

127
00:08:45,030 --> 00:08:46,200
It was your sister's secret help

128
00:08:46,200 --> 00:08:47,390
that made Li Nai defeat Jiang Jie.

129
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:49,000
- Is it also true?
- Watch your mouth.

130
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:51,720
Cui's family is special in the Alliance,
is it your plan to help Li family come back?

131
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:53,200
Did Cui Jing really cheat
in the challenge?

132
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:53,910
Please answer it.

133
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:54,960
Answer it please.

134
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,360
Wait!

135
00:09:07,700 --> 00:09:10,720
Ms. Cui,
did you really cheat in the challenge?

136
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:12,030
Can you explain it?

137
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:14,080
How was it even possible
that Li Nai won the game?

138
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:15,120
Ms. Cui!

139
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:16,600
Cui Can, get off!

140
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:23,120
Did Cui Jing really cheat?

141
00:09:23,510 --> 00:09:25,910
Xiu, even you don't believe me?

142
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:27,390
Do you know how much harm it did

143
00:09:27,390 --> 00:09:29,030
to my brother?

144
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:30,790
Why did she cheat?

145
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,630
Did you make her?

146
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,030
I didn't.

147
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,750
I don't know why it became like this.

148
00:09:36,360 --> 00:09:37,320
Xiu, you have to believe me.

149
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,240
I really have no idea.

150
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:41,270
Then go figure it out.

151
00:09:42,150 --> 00:09:43,870
If someone cheated,

152
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,550
the challenge can be restarted.

153
00:09:47,061 --> 00:09:47,636
Okay.

154
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,960
(Finally you answer my phone.)

155
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,360
Sorry, Ms. Cui.

156
00:10:00,630 --> 00:10:02,120
I was in the meeting.

157
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,630
It's just over.

158
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:06,510
You seem to have figured out
how to explain.

159
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:09,600
I hope you are not that kind of person
who burns the bridge.

160
00:10:09,630 --> 00:10:10,720
(Don't get me wrong, Ms. Cui.)

161
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:13,440
I have nothing to do with it.

162
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,150
Hardly had I reached an agreement with you

163
00:10:16,150 --> 00:10:18,120
when I was questioned for cheating.

164
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:21,030
(How can I believe you?)

165
00:10:23,550 --> 00:10:26,270
The media are just making
groundless accusations.

166
00:10:26,630 --> 00:10:27,720
(Listen to me,)

167
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:30,790
I work with you for long-term benefits.

168
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:33,320
Why would I give up
such a strong partner like you

169
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:35,480
only for Jiang Jie?

170
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:38,030
But now I, the whole Cui family,

171
00:10:38,030 --> 00:10:40,120
and even my brother have been pushed
in the teeth of the storm.

172
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:41,510
It is a solid truth.

173
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:43,480
(Don't you forget)

174
00:10:43,600 --> 00:10:46,440
who got me in trouble.

175
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,440
Please rest assured.

176
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,320
I'll take care of it soon.

177
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:53,260
I voted for Li Nai instead of Jiang Jie
who I should've voted for

178
00:10:53,270 --> 00:10:54,600
because I trusted you.

179
00:10:54,630 --> 00:10:55,720
(So Mr. Jiang,)

180
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,440
don't let me down.

181
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:00,630
Jing.

182
00:11:01,510 --> 00:11:02,320
Cui Can?

183
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:04,320
When did you come?

184
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,000
You really cheated on voting?

185
00:11:08,550 --> 00:11:09,270
Xuyang,

186
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:12,720
Cui Jing is obviously dragging you
into this.

187
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:15,550
It's simply like a a piece of cake
for Cui family.

188
00:11:15,630 --> 00:11:17,240
If she doesn't want drag me into this,

189
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,750
it'll really worry me.

190
00:11:19,150 --> 00:11:20,270
At least it seems

191
00:11:20,270 --> 00:11:22,630
Cui family wants to work with me
sincerely.

192
00:11:22,870 --> 00:11:24,630
Now we've got rid of Jiang Jie,

193
00:11:25,480 --> 00:11:28,390
then Cui Jing would be a key
to my next step.

194
00:11:31,480 --> 00:11:32,960
I know what you want, Xuyang.

195
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,390
I'll help you.

196
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:41,270
Who were you speaking to?

197
00:11:41,510 --> 00:11:43,630
It's obviously not for me.
Who made you do this, Jing?

198
00:11:45,030 --> 00:11:46,240
It's none of your business.

199
00:11:46,790 --> 00:11:48,480
Are you kidding?

200
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:50,120
Did you hear the voice outside?

201
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,550
They asked me if my sister had cheated.

202
00:11:51,550 --> 00:11:52,960
How should I respond to this?

203
00:11:53,240 --> 00:11:55,360
Don't you also wanna seize the knife back
for your master?

204
00:11:55,790 --> 00:11:58,200
Do you want me to tell the reporters this?

205
00:11:58,240 --> 00:12:01,320
Then you and Li Nai
hand Xue Congming's knife to Jiang Jie!

206
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,150
What's this?

207
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:11,480
I've always been treating you
as a child before,

208
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,120
but I was wrong.

209
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:16,630
You should know what trouble
Cui family got into right now.

210
00:12:21,869 --> 00:12:23,080
(Property Mortgage Contract)

211
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:24,790
Cui family's knife factory debt repayment?

212
00:12:25,910 --> 00:12:26,960
How did this happen, Jing?

213
00:12:27,320 --> 00:12:28,000
Can,

214
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:30,720
Cui family is in grave danger.

215
00:12:30,720 --> 00:12:31,960
I had to do this.

216
00:12:32,510 --> 00:12:34,720
Mutual help is Cui family's precept.

217
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:37,200
As long as you keep silent about this,

218
00:12:37,670 --> 00:12:39,000
we'll get through this difficulty soon.

219
00:13:12,120 --> 00:13:12,960
Nai,

220
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:15,030
why don't you have breakfast?

221
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:31,960
Uncle Li,

222
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,240
morning.

223
00:13:34,270 --> 00:13:34,870
Feeding fish?

224
00:13:35,240 --> 00:13:36,030
Morning, Can.

225
00:13:36,670 --> 00:13:37,600
I'll get you some drink.

226
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:38,870
No.

227
00:13:38,870 --> 00:13:40,000
I'm good.

228
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,120
Cui Can.

229
00:13:45,550 --> 00:13:48,910
How did it go with the cheating issue?

230
00:13:49,120 --> 00:13:50,120
It's nothing.

231
00:13:50,630 --> 00:13:51,870
They are just jealous of you.

232
00:13:52,320 --> 00:13:55,000
You mean your sister didn't cheat?

233
00:13:55,120 --> 00:13:55,960
Of course not.

234
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,120
I asked her in person,

235
00:13:57,270 --> 00:13:58,440
and the answer was definitely no.

236
00:13:58,960 --> 00:13:59,790
So Li Nai,

237
00:14:00,120 --> 00:14:02,120
you won fair and square.

238
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:03,790
Our master's knife

239
00:14:03,870 --> 00:14:04,960
will never be seized away.

240
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,120
I'm relieved a lot.

241
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,240
I still can't believe that

242
00:14:12,750 --> 00:14:14,240
I defeated Jiang Jie.

243
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:22,550
Cui Can.

244
00:14:23,870 --> 00:14:24,600
What's wrong with you?

245
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:26,000
Nothing.

246
00:14:26,630 --> 00:14:27,150
Right.

247
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,720
I gotta go.

248
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,000
I have a date with Xiu.

249
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,381
Go ahead.

250
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:32,750
Bye, Uncle Li.

251
00:15:21,870 --> 00:15:22,790
What are you doing here?

252
00:15:24,630 --> 00:15:25,720
I need to tell you something.

253
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:32,360
My brother wanna seize your knife
because of me.

254
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:35,120
He wanted you to take care of me.

255
00:15:35,670 --> 00:15:37,080
If I hadn't begged you,

256
00:15:37,870 --> 00:15:39,390
you would have agreed.

257
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,960
I agreed to your request,

258
00:15:42,510 --> 00:15:44,550
but you didn't stay
by your brother's side.

259
00:15:44,670 --> 00:15:45,910
It's the same now.

260
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:48,270
Even if you made him return the knife,

261
00:15:48,870 --> 00:15:49,630
it would

262
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,790
change nothing at all.

263
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:53,720
Back then

264
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:55,510
I wasn't able to help you,

265
00:15:57,630 --> 00:15:58,870
including your father.

266
00:16:03,320 --> 00:16:04,390
This is it.

267
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:08,120
Xue Congming didn't let me tell you,

268
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:10,200
but I think

269
00:16:12,240 --> 00:16:14,270
you should know the truth.

270
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:32,750
Sorry.

271
00:16:33,910 --> 00:16:35,600
Sorry, Jie.

272
00:16:38,630 --> 00:16:39,790
It's not your fault.

273
00:16:57,740 --> 00:17:00,020
(Thief! Cheating! Go to hell!)

274
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,030
Jiang Jie.

275
00:17:24,030 --> 00:17:24,590
You...

276
00:17:28,550 --> 00:17:29,510
Don't follow me.

277
00:17:34,030 --> 00:17:35,105
(Jiang's Residence)
Where is Xiu?

278
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,920
Jiang Jie got hurt.

279
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,790
Xiu was there with him the whole night.

280
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:40,960
Just for a woman,

281
00:17:41,640 --> 00:17:42,920
