282
00:17:43,750 --> 00:17:45,110
and even got into hospital.

283
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:49,110
What a good-for-nothing!

284
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,720
Grandpa.

285
00:17:54,790 --> 00:17:57,110
