289
00:18:05,830 --> 00:18:06,480
Okay.

290
00:18:07,510 --> 00:18:08,920
Dad will be happy.

291
00:18:26,310 --> 00:18:28,310
Jiang Jie got hurt so bad for you,

292
00:18:28,640 --> 00:18:30,030
