296
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,400
Sorry.

297
00:18:40,550 --> 00:18:42,000
Have you heard of the story of Yao family?

298
00:18:43,070 --> 00:18:47,270
Jiang Jie told me it was made up
to mirror Jiang family.

299
00:18:47,590 --> 00:18:49,480
The story actually meant that

300
00:18:49,480 --> 00:18:51,790
