after he had made a mistake.

301
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:54,310
What if his father never made a mistake?

302
00:19:06,270 --> 00:19:07,750
I'll tell you

303
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,270
a real story.

304
00:19:10,070 --> 00:19:12,680
Jiang family was the champion
of the seven families in Baichuan.

305
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:16,440
Jiang Ziqing, the host of the family,
had a pair of twin boys.

306
00:19:17,070 --> 00:19:18,440
(Jiang Yuanshan, the elder one,)

307
00:19:18,830 --> 00:19:20,030
(was Jiang Jie's father.)

308
00:19:20,240 --> 00:19:22,880
(He was not much of a gifted child,
but he'd never been troubled by that.)

309
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:25,070
(He just got married and bore children
like the most people.)

310
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:27,680
(He had a boy and a girl,
and they were very cute.)

311
00:19:28,270 --> 00:19:30,110
But Jiang Yuanfeng, Jiang jie's uncle,

312
00:19:30,310 --> 00:19:31,440
was super gifted

313
00:19:31,640 --> 00:19:32,920
but also arrogant.

314
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,480
He competed with others everywhere.

315
00:19:35,750 --> 00:19:38,000
(Finally he got defeated in a game.)

316
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:40,830
(Jiang Ziqing had to save Jiang family's
glory and reputation,)

317
00:19:40,830 --> 00:19:41,510
(Jiang Residence)

318
00:19:41,510 --> 00:19:43,830
(but he didn't want to give up
the more gifted son.)

319
00:19:44,400 --> 00:19:46,400
(So he got an idea.)

320
00:19:46,550 --> 00:19:48,440
(He made his twin sons)

321
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,960
(Jiang Yuanshan and Jiang Yuanfeng)

322
00:19:50,240 --> 00:19:51,160
(exchange identity.)

323
00:19:51,640 --> 00:19:53,440
So the one who competed with Ge Qunshan

324
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,000
wasn't Jiang Jie's father.

325
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:59,310
How could he treat his son like that?

326
00:19:59,480 --> 00:20:00,790
For one's own sake,

327
00:20:01,200 --> 00:20:02,400
