328
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:05,880
That why Jiang Jie wanted to
challenge Jiang family.

329
00:20:06,030 --> 00:20:07,920
It's all for his father.

330
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:14,830
Jiang Jie's father is best tempered man
I've even seen.

331
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:17,000
Besides, after he had been expelled
from the family,

332
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,880
he promised Jiang Ziqing

333
00:20:19,480 --> 00:20:22,070
