334
00:20:22,270 --> 00:20:24,640
Then how did Jiang Jie's father die?

335
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,550
Let's go back to Yao's story.

336
00:20:27,830 --> 00:20:30,830
Yao Zhengling and his wife and children
were expelled from the family,

337
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:33,790
but with his persistence and hard work,

338
00:20:34,110 --> 00:20:35,030
it took not long for him

339
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:37,070
to get a little reputation.

340
00:20:37,480 --> 00:20:38,680
But it had been not long

341
00:20:40,160 --> 00:20:41,830
before he got hurt in his hand.

342
00:20:48,440 --> 00:20:50,030
Jiang Jie, let's go.

343
00:20:50,830 --> 00:20:51,400
Get in there.

344
00:20:52,440 --> 00:20:53,110
What happened, dad?

345
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:54,750
Keep silent. Don't come out.

346
00:20:59,270 --> 00:21:00,160
What are you doing?

347
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,200
What are you doing?

348
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,400
What are you doing?

349
00:21:05,000 --> 00:21:07,270
Brother, don't blame me.

350
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:10,960
It's all because you always showed off
too much,

351
00:21:11,070 --> 00:21:14,440
