352
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,480
You're such a jerk!

353
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:28,240
(All this was caught by Jiang Jie
hiding behind.)

354
00:21:28,790 --> 00:21:31,480
Jiang Jie has been timid and introverted
since he was little.

355
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:33,750
His personality is completely different
from Xiu's.

356
00:21:34,030 --> 00:21:35,830
It's just back then in the welfare center,

357
00:21:36,440 --> 00:21:37,830
a friend told him

358
00:21:38,110 --> 00:21:40,030
if you got bullied one day...

359
00:21:40,270 --> 00:21:42,240
If you get bullied again,

360
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,030
you must get back at him.

361
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:46,510
Okay.

362
00:21:48,440 --> 00:21:49,790
Over these 18 years,

363
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:53,160
