382
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:30,310
- Yes.
- Everyone,

383
00:22:31,590 --> 00:22:33,350
about the knife-seizure contest between me

384
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:35,350
and Li Nai,
the Head Chef of Eating at Dusk,

385
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:40,000
