386
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,720
I did lose.

387
00:22:44,160 --> 00:22:45,030
So I hope

388
00:22:45,590 --> 00:22:47,000
this is it.

389
00:22:47,160 --> 00:22:48,110
Please go back.

390
00:22:48,440 --> 00:22:49,030
Thank you.

391
00:22:49,310 --> 00:22:50,550
