395
00:23:22,070 --> 00:23:22,790
Zheng,

396
00:23:23,440 --> 00:23:25,880
I owe you, and I'll pay you back.

397
00:23:29,070 --> 00:23:30,920
Though I'm elder than you,

398
00:23:31,270 --> 00:23:32,550
I've been always following you

399
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:34,720
