408
00:24:07,750 --> 00:24:08,750
There is never "if".

409
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:14,270
Xue Congming once

410
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:17,750
refused to take Jiang Xiu,

411
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:20,070
