it was all Jiang Xiu's idea.

412
00:24:21,550 --> 00:24:23,070
I misunderstood him.

413
00:24:24,160 --> 00:24:25,550
I owe him an apology.

414
00:24:28,160 --> 00:24:29,070
Now

415
00:24:32,590 --> 00:24:33,440
