416
00:24:56,480 --> 00:24:57,310
Li Jidong.

417
00:25:18,880 --> 00:25:19,400
Nai.

418
00:25:22,270 --> 00:25:22,960
Nai.

419
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:24,750
Jiang Jie...

420
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:27,590
Qiang Xie is gone.

421
00:25:29,030 --> 00:25:29,550
Nai.

422
00:25:29,830 --> 00:25:30,640
Don't cry.

423
00:25:31,160 --> 00:25:32,480
Qiang Xie will come back.

424
00:25:32,750 --> 00:25:33,680
Trust me.

425
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:35,200
Don't cry.

426
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:37,480
