427
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:40,880
He won't.

428
00:25:44,480 --> 00:25:45,440
Nai.

429
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:48,270
When you grow up,

430
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:49,510
